high_descs: turn right and go to the sink
At the sink pick the bottle off of the counter
Turn around and then go right to go to the toilet
Place the bottle on the back of the toilet
Turn around and cross the bathroom turn right and go back to the sink
Pick up the other bottle that is on the counter
Turn around and go right to the toilet
Place the second bottle on the toilet
anns.task_desc: Place both bottles on the back of the toilet

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the black vanity ahead.
Pick up the pink spray bottle in between the sinks on the vanity.
Turn around, hang a right at the wall and walk to the toilet ahead.
Put the spray bottle to the right of the left green candle on top of the toilet tank.
Turn around, hang a left at the wall and walk to the right side of the vanity ahead.
Pick up the pink spray bottle to the right of the sink on the vanity.
Turn around, hang a right at the wall and walk to the toilet ahead.
Put the spray bottle to the left of the right green candle on top of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Place two spray bottles on a toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn right and walk up to the bathroom sinks.
Pick up the purple spray bottle that sits on the countertop between the two sinks.
Turn around, walk up to the wall, then make a right to walk over to the toilet.
Place the spray bottle on the back of the toilet.
Turn around, walk to the door, then make a left and walk up to the far right bathroom sink.
Pick up the purple spray bottle that is on the counter, to the right of the right-hand side bathroom sink.
Turn around, walk to the wall, then make a right to walk over to the toilet.
Place the purple spray bottle on the back of the toilet, to the right of the other one.
anns.task_desc: Move two spray bottles to the back of the toilet.
